  "body": "### Component\n\nForge\n\n### Describe the feature you would like\n\nInstead of having to do:\r\n\r\n```solidity\r\n// forgefmt: disable-next-line`\r\nuint x = 100;\r\n```\r\n\r\nIt would be great to also support\r\n\r\n```solidity\r\nuint x = 100; // forgefmt: disable-line\r\n```\r\n\r\nThis inline syntax is pretty common, and is supported by prettier, ESLint, and likely others\n\n### Additional context\n\n_No response_",
